              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/bf8e655a65a1e61d133e9c59f9aef5b5_9177172260701105022.png",
                "key": "霜刃截击",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "霜刃截击"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">掠袭锐势</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/25e4bcd70e5c79ed88012c83939e6a12_2640853382547979124.png",
                "key": "掠袭之刺",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "掠袭之刺"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">本角色使用技能后：</span>对敌方出战角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>为（本技能最终伤害值-2）的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">生命之契</span>。（最多5层）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/1ab78a4e226b75e7739eee3d3b8ea8aa_5285793315548932183.png",
                "key": "血契掠影",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "血契掠影"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害<span>+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_8641254009244312294.png",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">掠袭锐势</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>对所有附属有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">生命之契</span>的敌方角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">生命之契</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色受到治疗时：</span>此效果每有1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>，就消耗1次，以抵消1点所受到的治疗。（无法抵消复苏、获得最大生命值或分配生命值引发的治疗）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，没有上限）。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7925321291264371428.png",
